) is housed at 
<collectionCode box="[596,686,1009,1035]" country="USA" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/142r-0w94" name="Smithsonian Institution, National Museum of Natural History" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="Museum">NMNH</collectionCode>
and has the following data label: 
